<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p class="lead">Your privacy is important to us.</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>
    We collect information you provide during registration (username, email) and 
    content you create (notes, ratings, comments).
</p>

<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p>
    Your information is used to provide and improve our services, authenticate your 
    account, and communicate with you about your notes.
</p>

<h3>Data Security</h3>
<p>
    We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including 
    password hashing and secure data storage.
</p>

<h3>Contact Us</h3>
<p>
    If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us.
</p>
